1. Save all the files in the structure shown above
2. Install the required packages:
   pip install flask pillow scikit-learn numpy

3. Run the application:
   python app.py

4. Open your browser and navigate to:
   http://127.0.0.1:5000/

The application will start in debug mode, which means:
- The server will automatically reload when you make changes to the code
- Detailed error messages will be shown in the browser

Usage:
1. Upload an image using the form on the home page
2. Select the number of colors you want to extract using the slider
3. Click "Generate Palette" to process the image
4. View the extracted color palette and copy color codes as needed